<% @client = Client.find(@order.client_id) %>
<% @user = User.find(@client.user_id) %>
<p><strong>This message was sent from a notification-only email address that does not accept incoming email. Please do not reply to this message.</strong></p>
<br/>
<p>Dear <%= @client.client_name.capitalize %>, </p>
<br/>
<p>You have a message with regards to the following signing:</p>

<ul>
	<li><strong>Signer/Client:</strong> <%= @order.borrower_1_first_name %> <%= @order.borrower_1_last_name %></li>
	<li><strong>NF Order #:</strong> <%= @order.id %></li>
	<li><strong>Escrow/Transaction #:</strong> <%= @order.loan_number %></li>
	<li><strong>Signing Date:</strong> <%= @order.signing_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
	<li><strong>Signing Time:</strong> <%= @order.signing_time %></li>
</ul>

<p>To view the message please go to <a href="http://www.notaryfly.com">NotaryFly</a> and log in with your username and password.</p>
<ul>
  <li>Username : <%=@user.email%></li>
  <li>Password : <%=@user.user_password%></li>
</ul>

<p>This information was provided by NotaryFly.com</p>
